ZH: 招标是一种公开的采购方式。
EN: Bidding is an open procurement method.

ZH: 这个项目需要进行招标程序。
EN: This project requires a bidding process.

ZH: 建筑公司正在进行新工程的招标。
EN: The construction company is bidding for a new project.

ZH: 公司负责人决定进行急需器材的招标。
EN: The company manager decides to conduct a bidding for urgently needed equipment.

ZH: 招标文件需要提交在截止日期之前。
EN: Bidding documents need to be submitted before the deadline.

ZH: 他们正在拟定招标公告。
EN: They are drafting the bidding announcement.

ZH: 招标过程应该是公正透明的。
EN: The bidding process should be fair and transparent.

ZH: 招标要求各投标方提供完整的文件和资料。
EN: Bidding requires each bidder to provide complete documents and information.

ZH: 对于招标结果，我们将尽快通知每个投标方。
EN: We will inform each bidder about the bidding results as soon as possible.

ZH: 这个项目的招标范围包括设备采购和施工工程。
EN: The scope of bidding for this project includes equipment procurement and construction.

ZH: 所有关于招标的信息都可以在我们的网站上找到。
EN: All information regarding bidding can be found on our website.

ZH: 投标人应该在规定的时间内制定招标计划。
EN: Bidders should prepare a bidding plan within the specified time.

ZH: 招标文件必须按照规定的格式填写和提交。
EN: Bidding documents must be filled out and submitted in the prescribed format.

ZH: 请在招标文件中提供详细的报价和技术方案。
EN: Please provide detailed quotations and technical solutions in the bidding documents.

ZH: 为了确保公平竞争，招标采用匿名评审的方式。
EN: To ensure fair competition, bidding adopts an anonymous review method.

ZH: 经过招标，我们选择了最佳的合作伙伴。
EN: After the bidding, we have selected the best cooperation partner.

ZH: 招标评审委员会将根据各投标方的资质和报价来进行评估。
EN: The bidding evaluation committee will assess the qualifications and quotations of each bidder.

ZH: 招标会议将于下周举行，请参加的人提前准备好相关材料。
EN: The bidding conference will be held next week, please prepare the relevant materials in advance for participants.

ZH: 招标的目的是为了找到最合适的供应商。
EN: The purpose of bidding is to find the most suitable supplier.

ZH: 我们希望通过招标过程来获得更好的合作条件。
EN: We hope to obtain better cooperation conditions through the bidding process.
